Title: Honor Their Sacrifice
Description:
There's nothin' we can do for the foragers the Primalists killed, but we can at least try an' provide some closure tae their kin.

See if ye can find anythin' of a personal nature on the fallen. I'm sure the Winterpelt will appreciate whatever ye can bring them.
ObjectivesText: Recover personal effects from the fallen Winterpelt Foragers.
